name: Individual Lumps of Coal
description:
They’re back for 2010! the ridiculous, hilarious, lumps of coal!

Chose an individual lump of coal that fits the personality of who you want to give it to! See all the lumps pictured and named. Each coal comes with a little story  (stories shortened for space in the listing) .

There’s Ricardo, the sneakiest…maybe the meanest lump of coal, who says ‘I’m in this stocking because you know you deserve it. You know what you’ve done.’

Betty, the sweetest, nicest coal, who says ‘…I heard that if you have a lump of coal in your stocking, that means you’re awesome!’

Maurice, the guiltiest, gentlest coal, who says ‘Oh goodness...I hope me being here doesn’t make you feel too bad….’

Tad, the raddest, baddest coal of all, who says ‘Me in your stocking is mark of pride, ’cause if i’m not here, it means you haven’t really been livin’

Georgina, the most energetic and well, slightly snarky coal, who says ‘…just don’t tell the guy in the red suit i’m here, cause he’s a big jerk and you won’t get any other presents!’

Want one of each? The lumps are sold as a full set as well!

name: Little Lumps of Coal Ornament Plush Set
description:
They’re back for 2010! the ridiculous, hilarious, lumps of coal!

A set of FIVE little coal lump guys and gals pictured can make an appearance in a stocking and then can become an ornament as well. Printed on organic bamboo jersey & stuffed with a little eco fill, Approximately 3" across. Their back is printed with “little lump of coal.”

This listing is for the full set of the little lumps of coal. Meet Tad, Maurice, Betty Ricardo, and Georgina. Each include a tag with their story. A couple examples of their (shortened) stories are as follows:

TAD – "...Having me in your stocking is a mark of pride, cause if I’m not here, it means you haven’t really been livin’.

BETTY – "…I heard that if you have coal in your stocking it means you’re awesome!"

RICARDO – "…I’m in this stocking because you know you deserve it. You know what you’ve done."

Interested in just one or two? i’ve set up a listing for them individually as well.
